Retrieves existing instances that qualify to be a target of this property, and instances that already are a target of the property and anchor! Returns an array with first the range class name, then those objects already in the range, then a 'null', and then all eligible objects.

Returns:
ExistingInstances, Serialisable object containing existing and potential instances for the range of this property

                               String property,
                               String[] date,
                               int dateCntr,
                               boolean updateText,
                               int type,
                               String key)
Updates the SG with the newly added date. If it's the first date, it increments the 'last operation' cntr; if it's the last, it updates and returns the feedback text.

Parameters:
anchor - int identifying anchor
property - property name
date - String array with date value added by user

type - type of session
key - browsing session key
Returns:
AnchorInfo[] with serialisable version of feedback text, or null if updateText was false or an error occurred
